esearch-HKD1000.jpg&h=a14d3a26&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:49:51.000Z","msg":"一千大元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34c4c92402366c6196ceea68b7627a0d2a01b2dd","tid":869611,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe8afd796a2985c2d1fdf57dfee88bc051c2bf38","tid":869611,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c22bb51f07d57c3fb9b46ec417db7ae8a633d5be","tid":869611,"uid":79563,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T08:22:36.000Z","msg":"講多無謂, 比錢先<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/2S467d9t/UK-research-HKD1000.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2F2S467d9t%2FUK-research-HKD1000.jpg&h=a14d3a26&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:49:51.000Z","msg":"一千大元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T15:11:56.000Z","msg":"小意思啦, 唔算係乜野錢黎, <br />\n<br />\n總之大家都加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f49ccbfa2ebbf3fd45bc5d1ad62379e9bda17ea","tid":869611,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c84ffefb41f7aed65f43614394f316242d2391a0","tid":869611,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fab02a191d41adf045840903b6b8e3c9d417bee7","tid":869611,"uid":171823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T05:13:45.000Z","msg":"想join有無得幫手？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T11:48:55.000Z","msg":"我記得之前佢地搞過 香港前途談判解密檔案 嘅 研討會<br />\n邀請公眾一齊將檔案整理成timeline<br />\n我都有去過下<br />\n不過無幾耐drop out 咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你可以主動去fb問下佢地嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n假如你響倫敦的話<br />\n咁佢地應該好歡迎你去幫手scan document"},"citedBy":0